== {rbtr_payor} Operations

[[rbtgo_payor_establish]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_attended axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_payor_establish}

Establishes
{rbtr_payor}
credentials and project configuration

[[rbtgo_ark_conjure]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_ark_conjure}

Conjures an
{rbtga_ark_image}
by building a container image
({rbtgog_ark})
from a vessel specification.
Build context delivered via {rbtga_ark_pouch}, submitted via `builds.create` API. The combined job produces both the `image` and `about` packages under the hallmark subtree (about steps embedded via stitch). Vouch is a separate Cloud Build job using DSSE envelope signature verification.

include::RBSAC-ark_conjure.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_ark_enshrine]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_ark_enshrine}

Enshrines upstream base images into
{gar_service}
({rbtgog_ark}),
producing content-addressed
{rbrv_image_anchor}
references from
{rbrv_image_origin}
declarations.
The
{rbtr_director}
submits a Cloud Build job that copies each upstream image by tag to GAR with a human-readable anchor tag, and writes the anchor back to the vessel regime.

include::RBSAE-ark_enshrine.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_ark_graft]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_ark_graft}

Grafts a locally-built container image into the
{rbtgi_repository}
({rbtgog_ark})
via native docker/podman push.
The image push itself is local (no Cloud Build); about and vouch follow as Cloud Build jobs.

include::RBSAG-ark_graft.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_ark_kludge]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_ark_kludge}

Kludges a locally-built container image for development iteration
({rbtgog_ark}).
No registry push, no Cloud Build, no credentials — `docker build` runs against the workstation cache and produces a `k`-prefixed
{rbtga_hallmark}
that composes cleanly with nameplate and compose infrastructure but is obviously not a production hallmark.
Kludge resolves
{rbrv_image_anchor}
declarations to GAR references identically to {rbtgo_ark_conjure}, but anchored images must already be locally cached; the credentialed fetch happens out-of-band via {rbtgo_image_retrieve}. Origin-only slots auto-pull inline — no credentials required for public upstream.

include::RBSAK-ark_kludge.adoc[]

